items.title: What we know about Austria school shooting
items.description: It is not yet known why a 21-year-old Austrian man committed a shooting that left 10 people dead.

items.title: Bomb attack plans found at Austria gunman's home
items.description: Police say they also found a non-functional pipe bomb and a "farewell letter" during a search.

items.title: Elon Musk says he regrets some posts about Donald Trump
items.description: The billionaire says his posts went "too far" after attacking the US president's planned tax and spending bill.

items.title: Who has been arrested by ICE under Trump?
items.description: Tens of thousands of people have been detained since Trump took office, including permanent residents.

items.title: Bodies of schoolchildren found after bus swept away by South Africa floods
items.description: A total of eight bodies, including that of the driver, have so far been recovered, an official says.
